<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Prescription / Vaccine Booking — 3‑Step Microflow</title>
    <meta name="description"
        content="A streamlined 3‑step booking flow prototype that reduces clicks and cognitive load compared to traditional 6‑step forms." />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
</head>

<body>
    <div class="back-nav">
        <a href="../../index.html" class="back-link">← Back to Portfolio</a>
    </div>
    <div class="wrap">
        <header>
            <div class="brand">
                <div class="logo" aria-hidden="true">NF</div>
                <div>
                    <h1>Prescription / Vaccine Booking</h1>
                    <div class="sub">3‑step microflow prototype (reduces typical 6 steps by combining choices +
                        auto‑defaults)</div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </header>

        <nav aria-label="Progress" class="progress" id="progress">
            <div class="dot active" data-step="1">
                <div class="num" aria-hidden="true">1</div> Service & Location
            </div>
            <div class="dot" data-step="2">
                <div class="num" aria-hidden="true">2</div> Date & Time
            </div>
            <div class="dot" data-step="3">
                <div class="num" aria-hidden="true">3</div> Your Details
            </div>
        </nav>

        <section class="card" id="step1" aria-labelledby="s1h">
            <h2 id="s1h">Step 1 — Choose service & location</h2>
            <div class="grid">
                <div>
                    <label for="service">Service</label>
                    <select id="service" aria-describedby="service-hint">
                        <option value="">Select…</option>
                        <option>Flu vaccine</option>
                        <option>COVID‑19 vaccine</option>
                        <option>Rx pick‑up consult</option>
                    </select>
                    <div class="hint" id="service-hint">Common services first. You can refine later if needed.</div>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <label for="location">Location</label>
                    <select id="location">
                        <option value="">Select…</option>
                        <option>Downtown Pharmacy</option>
                        <option>West End Pharmacy</option>
                        <option>Southgate Pharmacy</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="actions">
                <button class="btn" id="to2">Continue</button>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="card" id="step2" hidden aria-labelledby="s2h">
            <h2 id="s2h">Step 2 — Pick a date & time</h2>
            <div class="grid">
                <div>
                    <label for="date">Date</label>
                    <input type="date" id="date" aria-describedby="date-hint" />
                    <div class="hint" id="date-hint">Defaults to the soonest day with availability.</div>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <label>Available times</label>
                    <div class="slots" id="slots" role="group" aria-label="Time slots"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="actions">
                <button class="btn secondary" id="back1">Back</button>
                <button class="btn" id="to3">Continue</button>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="card" id="step3" hidden aria-labelledby="s3h">
            <h2 id="s3h">Step 3 — Your details & confirm</h2>
            <div class="grid">
                <div>
                    <label for="name">Full name</label>
                    <input type="text" id="name" autocomplete="name" />
                </div>
                <div>
                    <label for="email">Email</label>
                    <input type="email" id="email" autocomplete="email" />
                </div>
                <div>
                    <label for="phone">Phone</label>
                    <input type="tel" id="phone" autocomplete="tel" />
                </div>
                <div>
                    <label for="notes">Notes (optional)</label>
                    <input type="text" id="notes" placeholder="e.g., accessibility needs" />
                </div>
            </div>

            <h3>Review</h3>
            <div class="review" id="review"></div>
            <div class="actions">
                <button class="btn secondary" id="back2">Back</button>
                <button class="btn" id="confirm">Confirm booking</button>
            </div>
            <div id="err" class="error" role="alert" hidden>Please fill name and a valid email, and select a time.</div>
        </section>

        <section class="card" id="done" hidden>
            <h2>Booked!</h2>
            <p class="success">Your appointment is confirmed. A confirmation email will be sent shortly. (Prototype only
                — no email is sent.)</p>
            <p><a href="#" id="new">Book another appointment</a></p>
        </section>

        <section class="card" style="margin-top:18px">
            <h2>What makes this a “microflow”</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Combines steps:</strong> Service + Location (was 2 screens) → 1 screen. Date + Time picker
                    with smart defaults → 1 screen.</li>
                <li><strong>Smart defaults:</strong> Prefills the earliest available date and preselects the first open
                    slot after user picks a date.</li>
                <li><strong>Inline review:</strong> Shows a review card before confirmation to avoid a separate “review”
                    page.</li>
                <li><strong>Keyboard & screen‑reader friendly:</strong> Focus styles, ARIA labels, and clear headings.
                </li>
            </ul>
        </section>

    </div>

    <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>

</html>